name: Iron Man
description: Recovers from fatigue faster and has higher stamina.

name: Technical Wizard
description: Excels in technical wrestling, gaining a bonus in matches.

name: Brawler
description: Adept at brawling and hardcore matches.

name: Hardcore Specialist
description: Thrives in hardcore and no-disqualification matches.

name: Big Match Performer
description: Performs better in high-stakes and title matches.

name: Lazy Worker
description: Sometimes gives a subpar performance in matches.

name: Chemistry Master
description: Has great chemistry with a wide variety of opponents.

name: Crowd Favourite
description: Gains a bonus when performing in their hometown or in front of a large crowd.
